The paper discusses security risks and regulatory responses related to the industrial internet of things (IoT), specifically in the context of the smart energy supply chain. This suggests that the paper is likely to belong to the Computer Science sub-categories of Cryptography and Security (cs.CR), Information Retrieval (cs.IR), Software Engineering (cs.SE), Cybersecurity (cs.CY), and Systems and Control (cs.SY).
